The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic. Friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and a robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth for attention. As the event wraps up, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures.

Meanwhile, friends decompress on the quad, comparing their experiences and discussing which companies responded warmly. Students exit with tote bags and stacks of business cards.
